title: Wireless LAN Controller (WLC): Number of Wifi Connections
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/generic
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This checks display the number of connected clients in an wireless network.
 The check displays the number of clients per SSID and also one summary witht
 the total number of connected clients on all SSIDs.

 When using a Cisco device the client count per interface is shown in the
 service summary.

 Upper and lower levels can be set for each network via WATO.

item:
 Name of the SSID or "Summary" for the overall number of clients

discovery:
 One service is created for each wifi network and one summary service is created.
